Package org.monte.media.seq

Provides media handlers for the SEQ file format.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
SEQAudioCommand An SEQAudioCommand handles an audio command that is associated to a single frame of a SEQMovieTrack.
SEQDecoder SEQDecoder.
SEQDeltaFrame Represents a delta frame in a movie track.
SEQDemultiplexer SEQDemultiplexer.
SEQFrame Represents a frame in a movie track.
SEQMovieTrack A movie track gives access to the static resources of a movie (image and audio data, global informations).
SEQPlayer Player for Cyberpaint Sequence animations (*.SEQ).
SEQReader SEQReader.
SEQTrack SEQTrack.
 

Package org.monte.media.seq Description

Provides media handlers for the SEQ file format.

Atari "Cyber Paint Sequence" animations (SEQ).
